NITRO NINA broke a bit awkwardly and a length or so slowly, switched outside the leaders stalking that pair four wide into the turn, went three to four deep on that bend, kept on evenly in the lane and needed more. MS. MORENA switched off the inside, was five deep past the half, drifted out six wide by the end of the turn under urging, ran on willingly without being persevered with late. PAYNT THE MOON was outpaced and not a factor.
